<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Management System</title>
    <!-- Question 3a: Link CSS file to EJS template -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/app.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>🚀 Project Management System</h1>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px;">
            <p style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #7f8c8d;">
                Welcome to the Project Management System! Use weighted scoring method to evaluate and select the best
                projects for your company.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2d: Navigation links -->
        <nav class="nav-links">
            <a href="/projects">📊 View Projects</a>
            <a href="/projects/new">➕ Add New Project</a>
        </nav>

        <div
            style="background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 15px; margin-top: 30px; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
            <h2>📈 About Weighted Scoring Method</h2>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                The weighted scoring method helps you evaluate projects objectively based on four key criteria:
            </p>

            <div class="criteria-grid">
                <div class="criteria-item">
                    <strong>🏆 Competition (Weight: 0.1)</strong>
                    <p>Market competition level</p>
                </div>
                <div class="criteria-item">
                    <strong>💰 Potential Revenue (Weight: 0.3)</strong>
                    <p>Expected financial returns</p>
                </div>
                <div class="criteria-item">
                    <strong>💸 Cost (Weight: 0.2)</strong>
                    <p>Project implementation cost</p>
                </div>
                <div class="criteria-item">
                    <strong>❤️ Customer Value (Weight: 0.4)</strong>
                    <p>Value delivered to customers</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; color: #7f8c8d;">
                Each criterion is scored from 1-10, then multiplied by its weight to calculate the final project score.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>